{"tid":1512513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你真係選擇唔欺凌班警嘅細路 得罪講句你冇良知","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:46:32.000Z","uid":190579,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"097bfa94f7017fd25e1fae6c9e195a9aa108da9b","tid":1512513,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>良知很重要<br />\n但對沒有良知既人講良知<br />\n只會令邪惡既人無後顧之憂地迫害善良既人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>面對無辜手足每日被殘害</strong><br />\n仍然選擇保護敵人以換取心目中既光環<br />\n我地都只不過係個偽善嘅人<br />\n<strong>和沒有良知的人說良知 傻的嗎</strong><br />\n<br />\n作為一個目睹警犬暴行既人<br />\n我好相信每個警察最擔心既就係自己家庭<br />\n當自己個仔係寶，但當人地個仔冇老母<br />\n法律已沒有辦法制裁警犬<br />\n只有人民可以<br />\n<br />\n我琴晚見到叫人唔好欺凌個post<br />\n見住有800個正皮<br />\n我真係好失望 好失望 好失望<br />\n我見到大家都好明白遭受警暴者將會有咩心理創傷 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(強姦、全祼、毒打)</span></strong></span><br />\n一個唔小心 真係會尋死<br />\n細路仔同女人心靈有幾脆弱 <br />\n我地都做過細路 唔係唔知呀？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不要為了心中的「光環」犧牲無辜的人<br />\n請擇善固執 慎思而行<br />\n<br />\n對準目標 做正確的事</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.topnews8.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E5%B6%BA16%E6%AD%B2%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.topnews8.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25B6%25BA16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585.jpg&h=d8f979fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2019/8/048deptfiu4wuxim93ys08wwnp9ftm.jpg?h=628&amp;w=1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F8%2F048deptfiu4wuxim93ys08wwnp9ftm.jpg%3Fh%3D628%26w%3D1200&h=fe5e46b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6U6n1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6U6n1O.jpg&h=bc7c73a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100014623515014/videos/678433072654137/?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100014623515014%2Fvideos%2F678433072654137%2F%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=2d445da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100014623515014/videos/678433072654137/?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/applecitycrime/videos/904508716609363/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fapplecitycrime%2Fvideos%2F904508716609363%2F&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=786da8e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/applecitycrime/videos/904508716609363/</a>"},{"pid":"494411b501cd830ea3a03effff1a09473bc81ce8","tid":1512513,"uid":89145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68c26a074941ef269e681dbbfe92a37fdbb06936","tid":1512513,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=22f852ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=4bf80762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht